.signups-body
  .single-container	
    %header.single-header
      %h1
        =link_to "https://www.mercari.com/jp/" do
          %img(src="//www-mercari-jp.akamaized.net/assets/img/common/common/logo.svg?2296184308" alt="mercari")
      %nav.progress-bar.signup-bar
        %ol.clearfix
          %li
            会員情報
            .progress-status-first-red-line
          %li.active
            電話番号認証
            .progress-status-second
          %li
            お届け先住所入力
            .progress-status
          %li
            支払い方法
            .progress-status
          %li
            完了
            .progress-status-last
    %main.single-main
      %section.l-single-container
        %h2.l-single-head.registration
          電話番号認証
        %form.l-single-inner.registration-form{action: "https://www.mercari.com/jp/signup/sms_confirmation/", method: "POST", novalidate: "novalidate"}
          %input{type: "hidden", value: "", name: "after_save_callback"}
          .l-single-content
            .form-group
              %label(for= "nickname")認証番号
              %input.input-default{placeholder: "認証番号を入力", type: "number", value: "", name: "confirmation-number"}
              %p
                SMSで届いた認証番号を入力してください
            =link_to "http://localhost:3000/signups/address", class: "btn-default btn-red" do
              認証して完了
        %form.l-single-inner.registration-form{action: "https://www.mercari.com/jp/signup/sms_confirmation/", method: "POST", novalidate: "novalidate"}
          %input{type: "hidden", value: "", name: "after_save_callback"}
          .l-single-content
            .form-group
              %h3.text-left.l-chapter-sub-head
                30秒たっても認証番号が届かない方へ
              %p
                電話で認証番号を聞く事もできます。
            =link_to "http://localhost:3000", class: "btn-default btn-red" do
              電話で認証番号を聞く(通話無料)
        %form.l-single-inner.registration-form{action: "https://www.mercari.com/jp/signup/sms_confirmation/", method: "POST", novalidate: "novalidate"}
          %input{type: "hidden", value: "", name: "after_save_callback"}
          .l-single-content
            .form-group
              %h3.text-left.l-chapter-sub-head
                認証番号を再送することもできます。もう一度電話番号を入力して下さい。
              %p.l-single-text
                =link_to "https://www.mercari.com/jp/tos_list", target: "_blank" do
                  電話番号を再度入力する
              %p.l-single-text.text-center
                ※SMSが届かない場合は
                =link_to "https://www.mercari.com/jp/tos_list", target: "_blank" do
                  SMS受信設定
                を確認して、もう一度電話番号を入力してくださいしてください。
    %footer.single-footer
      %nav
        %ul.clearfix
          %li
            =link_to "プライバシーポリシー", "https://www.mercari.com/jp/privacy/"
          %li
            =link_to "メルカリ利用規約", "https://www.mercari.com/jp/tos/"
          %li
            =link_to "特定商取引に関する表記", "https://www.mercari.com/jp/tokutei/"
      %a.single-footer-logo{href: "https://www.mercari.com/jp/"}
        %img{alt: "mercari", height: "65", src: "//www-mercari-jp.akamaized.net/assets/img/common/common/logo-gray.svg?2296184308", width: "80"}
      %p
        %small
          &copy 2019 Mercari